  "text": "The top is MMP17. According to Puente et al [CITATION_1] , they revealed that MMP17 is expressed mainly in the brain, leukocytes, colon, ovary and testis, using northern blot analysis of polyadenylated RNAs isolated from a variety of human tissues. This implies MMP17 can be related with brain cancer.",
